ActNational Capital Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of MARCEL D. LEGAULT of Vaudreuil-Dorion, Quebec, as a member of the National Capital Commission to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Marc Letellier, whose term has expired.
